title: Midnight's Children - Salman Rushdie
description:
I have been doing my very level best to enjoy Rushdie's gushings of wit and malicious humour. My only source has been a CD rip and I simply cant get the wretched thing to play straight forwardly without so much of sliceing and dicing. ie. it plays file one of cd1 then file one of cd 2 - it gets the matrix on it's side. Confusing much?

In any event I am recompiling M'sC using ffmpeg. Midnight's children available on a single mp3 file only, for all to enjoy.
